  <brief_title>Selegiline Transdermal System for the Treatment of Cocaine Dependence - 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Trial of Selegiline Transdermal System for the Treatment of Cocaine Dependence</official_title>
  <sponsors>
